# Project Architecture & Context

Monorepo for VkSplat-based 3D Gaussian Splatting training research.

## Layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `ref/` | Frozen reference VkSplat (read-only ground truth; baseline tag `ref-baseline-2026-06-12`) |
| `ref/vksplat/` | Reference CMake/Python project root |
| `next/nlrc_vksplat/` | Clean-slate cross-platform rewrite (Phase 2 — all new work) |
| `test_data/` | Shared regression assets and golden masters (Phase 2) |
| `outputs/` | Training runs and buffer dumps (gitignored) |

## Testing

Rewrite verification: Catch2 + CTest harness (`nlrc_vksplat_tests`), fixture-first isolated GPU tests with invariant + ref-parity oracles. See `rewrite-testing.mdc`. Buffer/binding parity: `rewrite-buffer-contract.mdc`. Port sequence: `rewrite-porting-order.mdc`. Error policy: `rewrite-error-handling.mdc`.

## Targets

- **Windows x86_64** — MSVC or Clang via Ninja (`windows-debug` / `windows-release` in `next/nlrc_vksplat/CMakePresets.json`)
- **OpenHarmony ARM64** — OHOS NDK via Clang (`ohos-debug` / `ohos-release` in `next/nlrc_vksplat/CMakePresets.json`)

## Compute stack

- Vulkan 1.2+
- Slang for core compute pipelines
- GLSL 460 for radix sort only (`glslc --target-env=vulkan1.2`)

## Class hierarchy (conceptual)

`VulkanGSPipeline` → `VulkanGSRenderer` → `VulkanGSTrainer`

## Config propagation

**Rewrite:** `nlrc_vksplat_config.hpp` is SSOT; CMake profile options + `scripts/compile_shaders.py` emit embedded SPIR-V headers under `${CMAKE_BINARY_DIR}/generated/`. See `shader-build-embed.mdc`.

**Ref:** `vksplat_config.h` + runtime `.spv` load; see `ref/docs/shader-pipeline.md`.

